flowchart TD
    Start([割り込み発生])

    %% ===== Valley Interrupt =====
    Start --> Valley[INTRPT_DD_MTR_MotorControlValley]

    Valley --> RevCalc[回転数計算<br/>v_DD_MTR_CalcMotorRevolution_rpm]
    RevCalc --> EAngle[電気角推定<br/>u16_DD_MTR_EstimateEAngle]

    EAngle --> ADWait{AD0変換完了？}
    ADWait -- No --> ADTimeout[タイムアウト判定<br/>DelayフラグON]
    ADWait -- Yes --> CurrentCalc[相電流演算<br/>Iu, Iv, Iw]

    CurrentCalc --> OCDetect[過電流検出<br/>v_DD_MTR_DetectOverCurrent]

    OCDetect --> OCAbnormal{過電流異常？}
    OCAbnormal -- Yes --> GateOff1[強制Gate OFF]
    OCAbnormal -- No --> WireOpenEnable{断線検出有効？}

    WireOpenEnable -- Yes --> PPcalc[P-P電流算出<br/>v_DD_MTR_CalcCurrentPp]
    PPcalc --> WireDetect[断線検出<br/>v_DD_MTR_DetectWireOpen]

    WireOpenEnable -- No --> ValleyEnd
    WireDetect --> ValleyEnd

    ADTimeout --> ValleyEnd
    GateOff1 --> ValleyEnd
    ValleyEnd([Valley処理終了])

    %% ===== Peak Interrupt =====
    ValleyEnd --> Peak[INTRPT_DD_MTR_MotorControlPeak]

    Peak --> BattMon[バッテリ電圧監視<br/>v_DD_MTR_MonitoringBattVolt]

    BattMon --> ClarkePark[Clarke & Park変換<br/>Id/Iq算出]

    ClarkePark --> RegenDetect{回生過電圧？}
    RegenDetect -- Yes --> GateOff2[Gate OFF実行]
    RegenDetect -- No --> PIControl[電流PI制御<br/>v_DD_MTR_CurrentPIControl]

    PIControl --> InvPark[逆Park & Clarke変換]
    InvPark --> OverMod[オーバーモジュレーション]
    OverMod --> ClipPWM[PWM指令クリップ]

    ClipPWM --> GateCtrl[Gate制御]
    GateCtrl --> PeakEnd([Peak処理終了])